WEBVTT

00:09.970 --> 00:11.792
Ah huh? Haa.

00:11.875 --> 00:14.958
(Min): Whoa ho ho! -Maks kaslje kritikujuci-

00:18.625 --> 00:19.570
Sanites, da?

00:20.720 --> 00:21.696
Ugh! Pfft.

00:22.004 --> 00:22.867
Naae. Mat sita.

00:23.271 --> 00:25.410
Casupa ti. Ova sa ta-ta.

00:25.680 --> 00:27.195
Ha baba si, da?

00:27.284 --> 00:31.048
Esekita! Eh patika. Ah zizi!

00:31.125 --> 00:35.333
Eh wana ay. Eh sawa ti. Ah tita pata!

00:36.417 --> 00:37.667
(Maks): Dodi ovamo. (Min): Hmm?

00:37.750 --> 00:38.880
- Casa za vino se lomi-

00:39.229 --> 00:40.580
- Sa divljenjem- Prodavnica Parak.

00:45.334 --> 00:48.000
Ugh! Se Karik. Saka ting.
(U redu. Da vam ispricam pricu.)

00:48.000 --> 00:49.375
- Dramaticno- Et tone ekcoo.
(Jjednom davno,)

00:49.458 --> 00:51.083
Eh laka ti na ti qa.
(tu je bio sjajan camac.)

00:51.167 --> 00:52.333
Eh rocka tocka tick.
(A kada camac dode.)

00:52.417 --> 00:53.833
- Zlikovski- Eh yo qure kara!
(Zato sto se camac srusi!)

00:53.917 --> 00:55.625
Nyage siqo tacke.
(I onda su svi umrli.)

00:55.920 --> 00:57.000
- Maks vristanje-

00:57.818 --> 01:02.125
- U normalnom tonu- Jo pa sa tava! (Maks): Ah, siga stagher.

01:02.208 --> 01:03.458
Sepa takode!

01:03.938 --> 01:05.750
- Opako- Glorckling starttrick!

01:05.830 --> 01:08.083
(Maks): Eh para kiri gouratick (Min): -Smireno- Se passa.

01:08.170 --> 01:11.000
(Min): -Zaigrano- Katchu a ti-tat. (Maks): Pfft, ugh.

01:11.083 --> 01:14.792
Eh sa 'ugh'. Ba-- Batgar ha barsoba, da?

01:14.880 --> 01:19.625
(Min): 'Ah see tur, eh patuse.' (Maks): -Zaigrano- 'Toure-houre.'

01:19.709 --> 01:22.042
(Maks): 'Ana ma kin a poura doura.' -Min se ludo ruga-

01:22.125 --> 01:23.708
- Maks pocinje da se ruga- (Min): Marke bou!

01:23.792 --> 01:24.736
Ha tu tit.

01:25.225 --> 01:26.917
Pogledaj ovo, Danik. -Grmljavina tutnjava-

01:27.000 --> 01:28.333
(Min): Ugh! (Maks): Ugh!

01:29.680 --> 01:31.210
Ooh! Mmm.

01:31.290 --> 01:33.375
(Steve): Bo ro lat od ah Kuack. -Kuack nadrilekari-

01:33.470 --> 01:35.625
(Steve): Whoa, la ba li bi de Kuack. -Kuack nadrilekari-

01:35.708 --> 01:41.542
(Maks): Urgh! Kuack je prehlada. (Min): Eh sata ta-ta?

01:41.625 --> 01:42.667
(Min): Heh Sinqa Tong.
(Krezovi Pice.)

01:42.750 --> 01:43.958
(Maks): Zatick! (Cudoviste!)
(Min): Bleugh.

01:44.042 --> 01:44.917
(Min): Ta-ti! (Vodeci tockovi!)
(Maks): Zagh!

01:45.000 --> 01:47.375
(Maks): Mourkats! (Vjesalica!)
(Min): A ta-tara. (Leteca raketa.)

01:47.458 --> 01:48.583
(Maks): Urgh...

01:48.670 --> 01:50.167
(Maks): Krinka! (Vulkan!)
(Min): Asita. (Ptica u gnezdu.)

01:50.250 --> 01:51.583
(Maks): 'Pour le' Kralj.
(Min): Ma Dante. (Rainbov.)

01:51.667 --> 01:53.167
(Maks): Zaldor! (Unisti Zemlju!)
(Min): Mal Pato. (Muzicki simboli.)

01:53.250 --> 01:55.042
(Maks): Philip Cots.
(Min): Ma Toupit. (Odskacuce lopte.)

01:55.130 --> 01:56.167
- Maks se ruga-

01:56.240 --> 02:00.766
(Maks): Masiq et no et bleu.
(Min): Ta-ba ta-ba tou-be di? (Ovo tvoja glupa francuska sala?)

02:01.292 --> 02:03.500
Arata, azit!
(Dosta je, odlazim!)

02:05.595 --> 02:06.958
Eh, oh! Oh!

02:07.042 --> 02:07.486
Oye.

02:09.128 --> 02:10.000
Waha ah ha.

02:10.080 --> 02:12.125
(Maks): Ne, blah, ne. (Min): Et ca?

02:12.210 --> 02:13.833
- Mak dahne- Whoa! (Min): Da!

02:13.917 --> 02:16.375
(Max): Za Bornak. (Min): Proslost, takode smeh.

02:16.783 --> 02:18.917
(Min): Eh... (Oboje): Eh mnogo Sorpli!

02:19.000 --> 02:21.125
- Oboje veselo vristanje- (Maks): Whoa.

02:21.208 --> 02:23.667
Yo, ho, ho, ho. Ooh. Kuack! -Kuack nadrilekari-

02:23.750 --> 02:24.833
(Oboje): Kuack?!

02:24.917 --> 02:26.833
(Maks): Zaba goth. (Min): Ah suba ti-ta.

02:26.917 --> 02:30.083
Ticka sack. Ida ba tincka buot.

02:30.926 --> 02:33.080
- Obojica se kikocu-

02:33.167 --> 02:34.863
- Smijeh-

02:35.110 --> 02:37.566
- Maks adahne- 'Banezinkat'? (Min): Bada bouta vouda.

02:37.670 --> 02:38.875
Tou tou.

02:39.458 --> 02:41.042
- Kuack skripi na prozoru-

02:43.077 --> 02:45.750
- Automobili trube, Deca se igraju-

02:51.850 --> 02:54.042
- ♬ Zabavna muzika svira ♬-

03:02.000 --> 03:04.958
- Steve u panici stenjeno-

03:05.042 --> 03:06.080
- Pricanje i jecanje-

03:06.170 --> 03:07.330
- Kuack nadrilekari- (Steve): -Adahne od straja-

03:07.417 --> 03:10.040
- Kuack nadrilekari i tobolci- (Steve): -Drhtajuci- Kuack.
